  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1290.0,
      "end_time": 3360.0,
      "text": "Karl Marx is often described as one"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3360.0,
      "end_time": 6720.0,
      "text": "of the greatest thinkers of the 19th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6720.0,
      "end_time": 9260.0,
      "text": "His writings have inspired revolutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9260.0,
      "end_time": 11793.0,
      "text": "and generated centuries of fierce debate."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12690.0,
      "end_time": 14860.0,
      "text": "Born in Prussia, now Germany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14860.0,
      "end_time": 18810.0,
      "text": "in May 1818, Marx believed that capitalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18810.0,
      "end_time": 23010.0,
      "text": "which was in its infancy at the time, had serious flaws."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 23010.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "Marx claimed that in pursuit of profit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 29170.0,
      "text": "capitalists would encourage their ideology"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 29170.0,
      "end_time": 31810.0,
      "text": "that work is good, leisure is bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31810.0,
      "end_time": 34550.0,
      "text": "and material things will make us happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 34550.0,
      "end_time": 36250.0,
      "text": "Embracing mass production,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36250.0,
      "end_time": 38980.0,
      "text": "depriving workers of job satisfaction."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38980.0,
      "end_time": 42093.0,
      "text": "At the same time, exploiting the working class."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44080.0,
      "end_time": 46370.0,
      "text": "He became involved in the Communist League,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46370.0,
      "end_time": 48620.0,
      "text": "a small group of intellectuals who wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48620.0,
      "end_time": 51853.0,
      "text": "to abolish the class system and spread wealth equally."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52920.0,
      "end_time": 54960.0,
      "text": "Marx wrote The Communist Manifesto"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54960.0,
      "end_time": 59460.0,
      "text": "in 1847, with his benefactor Friedrich Engels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59460.0,
      "end_time": 62130.0,
      "text": "laying out the Marxist vision of a society"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62130.0,
      "end_time": 64223.0,
      "text": "where wealth is distributed evenly."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66130.0,
      "end_time": 71130.0,
      "text": "Property is owned publicly, and education is free for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72280.0,
      "end_time": 75640.0,
      "text": "But Marx was little-known and little-read at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75640.0,
      "end_time": 78930.0,
      "text": "When he died in 1883, only 11 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78930.0,
      "end_time": 80994.0,
      "text": "attended his funeral."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81840.0,
      "end_time": 84910.0,
      "text": "After his death, his ideas flourished."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84910.0,
      "end_time": 88300.0,
      "text": "Based on the theory of Marxism came communism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88300.0,
      "end_time": 92840.0,
      "text": "the realization of a stateless society where all are equal."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92840.0,
      "end_time": 95420.0,
      "text": "Communism became a global movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95420.0,
      "end_time": 97480.0,
      "text": "but the utopian ideal of a fair"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97480.0,
      "end_time": 101010.0,
      "text": "and equal society failed to materialize."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101010.0,
      "end_time": 104058.0,
      "text": "Communism tyrannized and impoverished it subjects."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104058.0,
      "end_time": 107010.0,
      "text": "And slaughtered them in the tens of millions."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107040.0,
      "end_time": 110550.0,
      "text": "Today, capitalism dominates the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110550.0,
      "end_time": 114373.0,
      "text": "But many of Marx's criticisms have never been more relevant."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115580.0,
      "end_time": 117860.0,
      "text": "Today, the global disparity between rich"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117860.0,
      "end_time": 119053.0,
      "text": "and poor is startling."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 120330.0,
      "end_time": 122880.0,
      "text": "Marx predicted that capitalism would lead"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122880.0,
      "end_time": 126170.0,
      "text": "to the rich getting richer and the poor staying poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 126170.0,
      "end_time": 127003.0,
      "text": "He was right."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 128449.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130829.99999999999,
      "text": "He also predicted that capitalism would lead"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130830.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132843.0,
      "text": "to boom and bust economics."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134540.0,
      "end_time": 138350.0,
      "text": "Marx predicted that capitalism would lead to globalization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 138350.0,
      "end_time": 139890.0,
      "text": "and that a handful of firms would"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139890.0,
      "end_time": 141803.0,
      "text": "have huge market dominance."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 143868.0,
      "end_time": 145670.0,
      "text": "However,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145670.0,
      "end_time": 148060.0,
      "text": "Marx underestimated the ability of"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148060.0,
      "end_time": 150650.0,
      "text": "capitalism to make everybody richer"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150650.0,
      "end_time": 153280.0,
      "text": "by making products much cheaper."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153280.0,
      "end_time": 155700.0,
      "text": "Since the 1980s, the number of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
