    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 166620.0,
      "end_time": 169293.0,
      "text": "that redistributed wealth through taxation."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171270.0,
      "end_time": 173830.0,
      "text": "Although there is a lot to learn from Marx,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
